reviewText: Loved the actress in this movie of course.  Movie quality at times was blurry and looked out of focus.  The ending of this movie not so happy.
The movie is wonderful, suspenseful and mesmerizing. Sushmita Sen is one of my favorite actresses not to mention that she was Miss World and Miss Universe.

This is a great non-musical drama from Bollywood starring the gorgeous Sushmita Sen. She really shines in her dramatic role. I normally can figure out these types of movies long before the credits roll but the ending came as a surprise to me. Fast paced well acted film. Well done! I highly recommend it.
